This passion wrought out in your life is the great miracle which is God’s reward for such prayer and fast and almsgiving as have for motive‚ not the keeping of the laW‚ but communion with him.’' The test and result of this passion is not feeling or zealous preaching‚ but the acting out toward men of the love principle which will cause saith to persist through all storms, all changes in the appearance of truth‚ all shocks of new knowledge, all throes of development—- a house on the rock, a home for the possessor, and a shelter for all who need his aid.
